議是別人需要遵守的，不是中國需要遵守的」。他續指，若他當時說租賃香港的條約不再適用，只是一份歷史文件，中國官員會理直氣壯地反對這說法。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"【Twitter戰線】每一retweet 我捐五毛落運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696968</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"47d22ce3aa88e652ca3a8b4e6d4b89704a7f38b5","tid":1697060,"uid":263563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d2d9ef88623b9ea873d01331b3c15206445b0bf1","tid":1697060,"uid":65530,"like":54,"dislike":3,"score":51,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:02:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:25:16.000Z","msg":"冇得活喺肥彭時代<br />\n但睇番歷史都想返去<br />\n<br />\n【Twitter戰線】每一retweet 我捐五毛落運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696968</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f1928c745b144e24b98bc0db044b6e566ddffef","tid":1697060,"uid":35804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:25:20.000Z","msg":"幫幫忙做啲嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足死嘅死傷嘅傷喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4918fe403b060502a5201b16066d32175ef441","tid":1697060,"uid":263563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f47ecbf413cd498d615208c1ff72320dc6938a3c","tid":1697060,"uid":171446,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:25:36.000Z","msg":"無變condom<br />\n<br />\n【Twitter戰線】每一retweet 我捐五毛落運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696968\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696968</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6761296edb35686c405aef89adf5ac2da3199faf","tid":1697060,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T15:26:01.000Z","msg":"外父感受最深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91f274b00143ad70b0a00cec5f3972d988f75b7","tid":1697060,"uid":288478,"l